Description_lang: Shrinekeeper Qanosh flings volatile lava at all players within $A1 yards, inflicting $407249s1 Volcanic damage to all enemies within $407249A1 yards of the impact and conjuring a lava puddle at the impact location. After $407249d, the puddle explodes and inflicts $407251s1 Shadowflame damage to all enemies within $407251A1 yards. If a player touches the puddle, the explosion will trigger automatically.
